<paragraph blockId="3.[151,1436,151,799]" pageId="3" pageNumber="147">
A discriminant analysis based on the shell measurements (D, D 
<number box="[881,894,152,175]" pageId="3" pageNumber="147" value="3.0">3</number>
, H, ad, ah) of 
<taxonomicName box="[1049,1149,151,175]" class="Gastropoda" family="Lauriidae" genus="Leiostyla" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Stylommatophora" pageId="3" pageNumber="147" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="beatae">
<emphasis box="[1049,1149,151,175]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="147">L. beatae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName box="[1163,1260,151,175]" class="Gastropoda" family="Lauriidae" genus="Leiostyla" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Stylommatophora" pageId="3" pageNumber="147" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="silicea">
<emphasis box="[1163,1260,151,175]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="147">L. silicea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName box="[1314,1436,151,175]" class="Gastropoda" family="Lauriidae" genus="Leiostyla" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Stylommatophora" pageId="3" pageNumber="147" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="paulinae">
<emphasis box="[1314,1436,151,175]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="147">L. paulinae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(
<figureCitation box="[159,227,186,209]" captionStart="FIGURE 2" captionStartId="2.[151,255,1936,1959]" captionTargetBox="[181,1416,688,1892]" captionTargetId="figure@2.[180,1416,687,1892]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURE 2. Separation of Leiostyla beatae n. sp., Leiostyla silicea and Leiostyla paulinae according to the first two discriminant functions based on shell measurements." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/235958/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="147">
Fig. 
<number box="[213,227,186,209]" pageId="3" pageNumber="147" value="2.0">2</number>
</figureCitation>
